Showcase Time: 6:41.100 - Plar

bhop_uncanny - is a huge experiment where I've challenged myself in detailing & texturing other peoples levels.


What exactly is this project about?

  • Participants created some gameplay with dev/nodraw textures only.
  • My goal - detail everything and make It look at least somewhat good.
  • Contribute with a rare kind of a map -> High-Tier & Great Visuals.


Challenge for Loshadka (streamer):

Requirements: 
- Beat the map on Normal style in under 1 hour (Multiple attempts)
- Stream your gameplay
- Show your received prize later (in Bihop or on Stream)

Prize (Dodopizza):
- Pizza
- Dodster OR Starter
- Drink
